title: Medani foresight
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

You gain a limited ability to see into the immediate future. This spell takes about one minute to cast. For 1 hour, you can't be surprised and you have a large [[advantage]] on all attempts. This spell immediately ends if you cast it again before its duration ends.

(See also [[foresight]].)